Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Quadratic Implementations", "TechNoteSection",
 CellID->1081937375,ExpressionUUID->"df3e54af-593a-49e1-b026-6d5ae7b4c59c"],

Cell["\<\
Here we introduce two methods to implement multi-control unitary gates in \
terms of elementary gates the computational cost of which grows quadratically \
with the number of control qubits (Barenco et al., 1995).\
\>", "TechNoteText",
 CellID->425570584,ExpressionUUID->"d6d83aa0-d36d-417e-9e5c-3566f1ab6a9e"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "\tThe first method is based on the idea that has also been used for an \
implementation of the ",
 ButtonBox["Toffoli gate",
  BaseStyle->"Link",
  ButtonData->"paclet:QuantumMob/Q3/tutorial/MultiControlNOTGate#770299810"],
 " and of the ",
 ButtonBox["multi-control NOT gate",
  BaseStyle->"Link",
  ButtonData->
   "paclet:QuantumMob/Q3/tutorial/MultiControlNOTGate#1310796799"],
 " with more control qubits. Given a unitary operator ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["U", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "367561b4-8eda-4d19-9f24-7ebc23405c96"],
 " on the target qubit, the implementation of the ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["n", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "87800814-6412-4bde-9acc-e0e77bb26426"],
 "-control ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["U", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "02dbb4d0-3e8f-4e4e-9a1c-cef5652b005c"],
 " gate using this method is summarized in Figure 3. Let ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["V", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "b6a0763a-c435-41a8-a9dd-2260e89393ed"],
 " be a unitary operator such that ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"U", "=", 
    SuperscriptBox["V", "2"]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "8568ddca-2e54-4c39-ab27-549602b49c8b"],
 ". The center piece between the vertical dashed lines in the quantum circuit \
on the right-hand side represents a conditional unitary operator that \
operates ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox["V", "\[Dagger]"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "9654aff4-a4f2-46d0-add8-57f2098f5189"],
 " on the target qubit only when either (but not both) each of the first ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"n", "\[Minus]", "1"}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "dcb59487-04e8-4b43-98aa-52670fc7eddb"],
 " control qubits or the last control qubit is set to |1\:27e9. Combining \
this piece with a single-control ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["V", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "09f1115f-8411-4849-956b-9f241b05a056"],
 " gate and a ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"(", 
    RowBox[{"n", "\[Minus]", "2"}], ")"}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "1e7640ce-8946-4c76-bc2d-bbd124c017bd"],
 "-control ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["V", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "0e312c82-8e3a-4ff3-907d-42c69478fbdb"],
 " gate, one can rebuild the desired ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["n", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "dae7b581-69a4-433c-bfdf-6601cf2ccc49"],
 "-control ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["U", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "749d1f9c-ba65-4d93-a7fa-0b709c7ec2b3"],
 " gate."
}], "TechNoteText",
 CellID->512596961,ExpressionUUID->"9aa52996-8a2b-48cc-bc6f-d56e70e595dc"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "\tThis method requires two ",
 ButtonBox["multi-control NOT gates",
  BaseStyle->"Link",
  ButtonData->"paclet:QuantumMob/Q3/tutorial/MultiControlNOTGate"],
 ", each of which entails ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"\[ScriptCapitalO]", "(", "n", ")"}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"c9546c5c-2658-4785-ad68-a518904f3094"],
 " elementary gates. It is still to recursively implement ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"(", 
    RowBox[{"n", "\[Minus]", "2"}], ")"}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "ece05fbc-84a6-461d-94c7-050f1cdd55a7"],
 "-control ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["V", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "682b77a3-ef4b-4b01-bad3-8c65ac364961"],
 " gate. The recursion relation of the computational cost reveals that the \
overall cost of the implementation is quadratic in ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["n", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "28f06a11-3678-444c-b39a-8e12568a9ef3"],
 ", that is, ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"\[ScriptCapitalO]", "(", 
    SuperscriptBox["n", "2"], ")"}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "431dfa95-b1b4-4486-9065-4e73f2d15e3c"],
 "."
}], "TechNoteText",
 CellID->1350340999,ExpressionUUID->"faf8b4a9-377a-45b6-a575-5a00cf80e4ed"],

